message.body: Aww! Jenny's engaged!?!
Yeppers!!
That's so crazy. Thoughts?
I'm happy for her. They're not gonna tie the knot anytime soon. They're gonna wait till she's done school
Aww! That's so great, yes planning a wedding and school is too hard. I can't believe they have been together that long. Did you know he was going to propose?
Not a clue haha
Ut oh. He didn't ask your dad?
No lol but my mom and dad are happy about it
Okay good. Made me nervous haha
I know! Lol he was gonna ask the day of my birthday party but he didnt catch his bus.
Oh really? No I like this way much better haha
Yeah haha
Ah!!!! Omg! Congratulations! I'm so excited for you, when?
The 16th.. I'm nervous about it lol
Oh good you have some time, listen you are the smartest person I know. You're dedicated and passionate. They will love you! You've got what they want or they wouldn't offer you the interview
Aw thanks!
I only speak the truth. And I'll be sure to tell you that before the interview :)
You're the best!
You're my girl! I got you!
I just spent tons of money on summer clothes tonight and yet I still have no idea what to wear to maroon 5!
I haven't even thought about what I'll be wearing lol
I usually don't until day of but I was putting stuff away and realized I don't have anything.
Me neither lol
I think I have this one shirt but I don't have shoes I like.
I'm so excited for this week. I have seriously just wanted to dance all week.
Hahaha awesome!
Yes! Haha I get in my moods that i just want to go to a club and dance but no one is ever interested
Aw that sucks lol
